626
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:48,840
your future.

627
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:49,760
You know? Ziqiu.

628
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:51,880
I live abroad now.

629
00:25:52,080 --> 00:25:53,080
Go abroad with me.

630
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,560
You can go to

631
