00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,320
That's funny.

695
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:44,920
OK. OK.

696
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:46,000
We'll go there during the summer holiday.

697
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:46,560
OK. OK.

