00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:57,080
Don't affect them.

706
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:58,440
It doesn't matter.

707
00:27:58,880 --> 00:27:59,400
Thank you, Dad.

708
00:27:59,600 --> 00:28:00,320
Eat. Eat.

