743
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:13,640
Well.

744
00:29:14,600 --> 00:29:15,320
Do you still remember

745
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:17,120
Zhao Huaguang?

746
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,560
