749
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,520
I haven't heard about that.

750
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,080
Zhao Huaguang's dad

751
00:29:34,080 --> 00:29:34,880
is over 70 years old now,

752
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:35,840
but he still works in the field.

753
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,240
I heard that

754
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,120
