756
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,320
He lives abroad now.

757
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,280
He almost becomes a foreigner.

758
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,600
There is just one mountain

759
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:47,080
between their hometown and ours.

760
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,080
It was particularly poor.

761
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,840
