765
00:29:54,560 --> 00:29:56,080
on building a bridge and a road for their village.

766
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:56,840
Now,

767
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:58,320
even trucks carrying vegetables

768
00:29:58,320 --> 00:29:59,360
